title.narrative: Sustainable Management of Agricultural Research and Technology Dissemination (SMARTD)

description.narrative: The objective of the Project is to improve the institutional capacity and performance of the Indonesian Agency for Agricultural Research and Development (IAARD) to develop and disseminate relevant and demand-driven innovative technologies, meeting the needs of producers and of the agri-food system.
